::The stressful situation has left its mark on this man's face - his skin has became so pale one would say that it has aged for several years over the past few minutes. With his fragile hands, he proceeds to wipe the waterfall of sweat flowing down his face. You can hear him mumbling something to himself as he turns around, making sure that everything is safe.::

I-I... thought twas all over... my life... flashin' before my eyes... ::He takes a deep breath.:: I got nothin' to say you... but thanks.
